  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0da9\u0dca \u0d91\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dad\u0dca \u0daf\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad \u0db4\u0daf\u0dca\u0db0\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u2018\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A 'hole' in the Covid vaccine data system",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Currently, the people are in a lot of trouble due to the fact that the vaccination record of the people who got vaccinated through the anti-covid vaccination program jointly implemented by the Ministry of Health and the anti-covid task force has not been properly entered into the program's data system.",
        "In many vaccination centers operated by the Office of the Medical Officer of Health and the security forces, although the vaccinations are recorded on the card and not included in the data system, people going abroad have to go to several places to present the card and enter it in the data system while obtaining the electronic report against 'Covid'.",
        "When people intending to go abroad go to the health doctor's office in the area of \u200b\u200bresidence to get the electronic report against 'Covid', they are informed to go to the places where they received the vaccinations and bring them into the data system and it is known that some people have to go to all three places where they received all three vaccinations.",
        "It is alleged that when people go to certain places, they have to spend hours in those places and people who are preparing to go abroad are in a lot of trouble due to this situation."
      ],
